<p>controller:</p>  <pre><code>onSelectRow :         function(id){              setTimeout(function () {$scope.getSelectedRow(); }, 0);           },};  $scope.getSelectedRow = function(){  var grid = $("#patientgrid");  var rowKey = grid.jqGrid('getGridParam',"selrow");  var kelr = grid.jqGrid('getCell', rowKey, 'PostTopic');  if (rowKey) {       $scope.lastsel=kelr;    } else alert("No rows are selected");} </code></pre>  <p>Html: </p>  <pre><code> &lt;h1&gt;Topic:{{lastsel}}&lt;/h1&gt; </code></pre>  <p>Problem is ... when I choose the new row, "lastsel" doesn't change.</p>